{
  "stem": "985.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father worked actually for him among a few other men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In August 1942, they took away my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was working out of the-- I call it out of the house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he found out that there was a round up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They took everybody to the railroad station where they have freight cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they load them up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And loaded them up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were about to leave that evening the following day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my father found out-- he and another man who was an engineer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Engelberg was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His daughter was also taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they both begged this Beitz if you could do something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So finally, they convinced him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he got into the car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he went to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When you saw the movie there was a scene where Schindler knocks on the doors of the freight cars and looks for the men of the name Stern.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, visualize in reality that is what happened in 1942.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This Beitz with a Gestapo officer knocking-- there was a noise, because of screams, and yelling-- knocks on every freight car.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he yells the name Klinghoffer, Klinghoffer, Engelberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Klinghoffer was the name of my mother and my mother and Engelberg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And finally, one of the car doors open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they grabbed my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As she was pulling my mother, an SS man shoved the door and pushed my mother back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the last of my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then he went to another car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he picked up this girl, Engelberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the two of them survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were taken to a home and subsequently they went through all kinds of different difficulties.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
